    "Section 4 is focused on the fundamental analysis of technologies for three different data tiers of a DPP: Data Collection, Data Curation and Sharing, and Data Leverage supported by previously proposed solutions and mechanisms that utilize the corresponding technologies.",
    "Meanwhile, it presents our proposed solution based on the initial technological research and associates the analyzed technologies with each component of the framework respectively.",
    "Section 5 utilizes the suggested framework through a representative use case scenario, by taking into consideration fundamental requirements and clarifying its impact.",
